PTorrent — Installation and Build Guide
========================================

Requirements
------------

  * Android Studio (Hedgehog or later) OR Android SDK command-line tools
  * Android device or emulator, API level 26+ (Android 8.0+)
  * adb (Android Debug Bridge) in PATH
  * Python 3.12 (for running aggregators locally)
  * Java 17+ (for Gradle / Android build)

Building the PtolemySeeder APK
-------------------------------

  The build script handles everything:

    cd android
    bash build_apk.sh

  This will:
    1. Run `./gradlew assembleDebug` inside android/PtolemySeeder/
    2. Output: android/PtolemySeeder/app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk

  Manual build:

    cd android/PtolemySeeder
    ./gradlew assembleDebug

Installing on Device
--------------------

  With device connected via USB (USB debugging enabled):

    bash android/build_apk.sh --install

  Or manually:

    adb install -r android/PtolemySeeder/app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk

Seeding a Corpus — Two Delivery Paths
--------------------------------------

  a) adb push to inbox/ (automatic pickup via FileObserver):

    adb push ptorrents/physics.ptorrent \
      /sdcard/Android/data/com.ptolemy.seeder/files/inbox/

  b) Tap to open — transfer the .ptorrent file to your device and tap it
     in any file manager. The Seeder registers as the handler for
     application/x-ptorrent and *.ptorrent files.

Pulling Trained Bin Files
--------------------------

  After seeding completes, pull the checkpoint files to your desktop:

    adb pull /sdcard/Android/data/com.ptolemy.seeder/files/monad_physics.bin     .
    adb pull /sdcard/Android/data/com.ptolemy.seeder/files/monad_mathematics.bin .
    adb pull /sdcard/Android/data/com.ptolemy.seeder/files/monad_english.bin     .

  Bin files go in bin_archive/clean/ if fresh GEOMETRIC INIT,
  or bin_archive/dirty/ if post-training checkpoints.

adb Workflow Quick Reference
-----------------------------

  Push updated corpus manifest:
    adb push android/corpus_list.json \
      /sdcard/Android/data/com.ptolemy.seeder/files/

  Add a new .ptorrent via inbox:
    adb push ptorrents/my_corpus.ptorrent \
      /sdcard/Android/data/com.ptolemy.seeder/files/inbox/

  Pull all bin files:
    adb pull /sdcard/Android/data/com.ptolemy.seeder/files/ ./pulled_bins/

  Check device logs:
    adb logcat -s PTorrent SeedService CorpusDetail

Running the Medical Aggregator (Linux/macOS)
--------------------------------------------

  Install dependencies:

    pip install requests

  Run:

    python aggregators/medical/scholar_aggregator.py

  Output: JSON with Ainulindale cancer-drug tags in the working directory.
  Set NCBI_API_KEY environment variable for higher PubMed rate limits.
